title: SPECIAL - NO APP FEE & $99 SECURITY DEPOSIT
posting_body: Come check out our beautiful community in the heart of Pioneer Square!
We are within walking distance of Pike’s Place, Lumen Field, and T-Mobile Park.
We are a high-rise building in downtown Seattle.
The main transit line is right across our building!
We offer units with beautiful views of the Puget Sound and downtown.
IN UNIT Washer and Dryer for all your laundry needs.
We also have in unit A/C for the hot summer days that are to come.
A 24-hour gym is located on our main floor as well as a common area to study, read, and relax.
There are many restaurants, cafes, and art studios located in the area.
We are currently running a special of NO APP FEE and $99.00 deposit upon approval.
Call us today to schedule a tour.
